Things needed:
pom.xml -: where you mention everything 
Project: 
GroupId: com.telusko -: define package :- all projects under this domain
ArtfactId: demo :- When we make project we need to make sure it is unique from the world. :- needs to be unique :- define your project name
Package: com.telusko.demo.web

Maven has 2 repo:
1. Remote
2. Local : will check here first and then download from the remote once conencted with the internet.

We get the code structure and the required dependencies 
Then when we save the code then we te the deecy installed in under our MAVEN DEPENDENCIES.


